            "body": "<p>what bout this?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>         Marks = input.nextInt();\n while (Marks &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; Marks &lt;= 100) {\n    System.out.println(\"Enter Students Test Marks Here\");\n\n    Marks = input.nextInt();\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 13670776,
